== For reading sources

: Source
~ Abstracted description of a source. Includes common actions, and gear for retrieving lines from a source, if possible.

: CodepointIterator
~ Iteraters for stepping through the codepoints of various sources 

: TrackingIterator
~ Tracks, in source-relative coordinates, centred on 0/0, the position of the iterator

: TokenIterator
~ Transforms the souce contents into a series of simple tokens. Bare bones, for extension

: 
